plot: While artifact-hunting with Pete, Myka spots the man who killed her former partner and resolves to bring him in. Meanwhile, Artie mind-melds with a dog.

Myka spots the elusive Leo, the man who killed her partner, which dredges up old emotions and leads Myka to uncover a bigger conspiracy. Claudia and Steve recover an artifact but are shot with tranquilizers before they can return it to the warehouse. The artifact is stolen, which raises the question - who took it?—David Foss
